Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.13,0:00:07.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯大人似乎遇袭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.38,0:00:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.76,0:00:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过听说没有受伤人平安无事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.10,0:00:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.51,0:00:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还不清楚详情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.31,0:00:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过据说是偶然被卷入了联合的内部纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.11,0:00:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是暗杀父皇那帮人干的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.36,0:00:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  阿莱克希斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.49,0:00:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才刚在大圣堂碰上那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯大人说无论如何都想跟马丽娜大人谈一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.34,0:00:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答应他的请求如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.21,0:00:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀父皇一事是精心策划的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.68,0:01:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿看见我们结婚的人引发了惨剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.98,0:01:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.86,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们注定无法结合啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.51,0:02:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.97,0:02:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然暗杀佩提力克那帮人使了这么大胆的招数啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.10,0:03:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来殿下果然还爱着马丽娜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.02,0:03:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.90,0:03:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道殿下跟马丽娜是怎么相爱的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.45,0:03:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  倒是听说过二人是在埃兰姆留学时认识的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.03,0:03:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  二人六年前在那里坠入爱河了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.46,0:03:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出十么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.38,0:03:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名男子坐在路中间不动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.47,0:03:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据穿着打扮来看应该是君主子弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.77,0:03:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是公共马车路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.14,0:03:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请您不要做危险的举动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.06,0:03:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铺石路的石头非常漂亮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.36,0:03:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反射太阳光之后一闪一闪的好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫阿莱克希斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.92,0:04:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫马丽娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.83,0:04:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫马丽娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.80,0:04:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道爱这个词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.26,0:04:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  看见你之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次明白了  它究竟是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.43,0:04:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你擅长的追求语句吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到了写给大小姐的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那人写的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你把它收起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.45,0:04:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.08,0:04:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么看上一封  写封拒绝的回信如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.75,0:04:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.85,0:05:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我此刻沉浸在知晓爱的喜悦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.85,0:05:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是它驱使着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.27,0:05:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜我要将花送给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.49,0:05:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说等下有使者要来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…玫瑰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.46,0:05:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚阿莱克希斯大人称前来送花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.30,0:05:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后突然开始摆石头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.88,0:05:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真是个有意思的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.27,0:05:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是必须回礼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.23,0:05:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说阿莱克希斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.56,0:05:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常出没于聚集着君主子弟的晚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.00,0:06:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稀客稀客  生面孔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发爵票亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰也够紧致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人有种想抱住的冲动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你别碰我好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你可没有兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.19,0:06:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的胆子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位小姐看上去很不情愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.66,0:06:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强迫可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.45,0:06:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是少碍我事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.86,0:07:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是在做梦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是做梦哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.45,0:07:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤很疼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.83,0:07:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见你一次后我确信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.75,0:07:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哈鲁西亚大公的公子阿莱克希斯对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.17,0:07:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.18,0:07:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来你为何会出席这场晚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为收到了美丽的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回礼所以就来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.35,0:07:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明知我的出身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.61,0:07:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何还会喜欢上我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在埃兰姆  家名无关紧要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.03,0:08:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与你相遇后  我动心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我知道了 这就是爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.75,0:08:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们是绝不可能结合的敌人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.88,0:08:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我无法违抗得知了爱的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.42,0:08:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单单是看过你的信我就感受到你的心意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.72,0:08:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉就像在看恋爱剧的剧本一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会以悲伤的结局告终
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这便是花的回礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我的初吻哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.87,0:08:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过你不珍惜也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们就这样结束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.21,0:08:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不打算再来见你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你希望如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.22,0:09:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我不会忘记你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.59,0:09:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的一切已经铭刻在我心中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.45,0:09:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是前往达希卿的宅邸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.25,0:09:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐请看车外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.34,0:09:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么最后再来一次可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.96,0:09:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.97,0:09:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已做好被训斥的觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.64,0:10:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过 我实在不忍看着大小姐消沉下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.52,0:10:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是多余的用心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.19,0:10:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此处距离阿莱克希斯大人的宅邸没多远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.16,0:10:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说他经常徒步来此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.28,0:10:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像那样与孩子和交流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好唱得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.71,0:10:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家收好银币回家去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.13,0:10:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.30,0:10:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.17,0:10:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那叫交流？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.72,0:10:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.06,0:10:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是将来要肩负起联合命运的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而你居然给孩子们发银币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.99,0:10:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你会满足吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是只要施舍与人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.83,0:10:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会出现不公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进而让统治出现裂痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我并不认为自己是在施舍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.88,0:11:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一开始的目的就只是我给的钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在不一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.47,0:11:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们很期待跟我一起唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.14,0:11:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.10,0:11:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,施舍是单纯地给予财物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然收取的人会感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.98,0:11:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过其中没有喜悦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.28,0:11:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让人们幸福地生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.03,0:11:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须让内心获得满足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.61,0:11:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并不是君主的职责啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.28,0:11:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不这么认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.62,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反倒觉得这是最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.87,0:11:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记这一点的统治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.67,0:11:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终将致使人民陷入不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是办不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.34,0:11:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这无非是理想罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.22,0:11:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便这理想是一条困难的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不断追寻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.60,0:11:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能无限接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.77,0:12:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何你能如此断言呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.02,0:12:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为刚才那些孩子变得会冲我笑了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.74,0:12:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心获得满足的统治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.83,0:12:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.64,0:12:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你决定什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.47,0:12:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定成为你的妃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.35,0:12:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我好像也爱上你了  没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道需要多少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.07,0:12:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我一定会前去接你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.49,0:12:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请你不要变心  一直等着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.03,0:12:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.87,0:12:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.24,0:13:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  我哪可能变心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.20,0:13:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只有你能填满我的心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.34,0:13:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边是我所知的二人相爱的过程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.89,0:13:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如是政治婚姻那我当时就反对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.22,0:13:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真心相爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就应该在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论身份如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.78,0:13:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  对佩提力克•罗西尼的处置就定为开除出联合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.41,0:13:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.66,0:13:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.70,0:13:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.74,0:13:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.78,0:13:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.83,0:13:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.87,0:13:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.91,0:13:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.79,0:13:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来该讨论道森公爵提出的议题了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.04,0:13:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为阿尔图克伯爵的行动有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.63,0:13:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然凭一己之见就跟大工房同盟幵战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.59,0:13:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致和谈变得困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.22,0:14:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让联合陷入了危机不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.05,0:14:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此关于开始战争的原委
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.06,0:14:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我的从者君主提欧•科尔内罗来说明吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.69,0:14:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.27,0:14:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.98,0:14:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经屡再三向斯达尔克的肯贝尔阁下发出归顺的通告了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可至今仍未给出答复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.99,0:14:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,归顺不仅是形式问题还需要精神上的联系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能轻易起誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.37,0:14:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是就凭我你的主人是无法认可的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是目前还不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.05,0:14:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要马丽娜大人展现出盟主的资质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必在下的主人就会下定决心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是要让我先展现出资质？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.02,0:14:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要在下的主人立刻归顺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么希望您能这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.40,0:14:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的说明到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.40,0:15:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是  提欧发起的战争并非针对同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.74,0:15:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流放有悖爵位制的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.24,0:15:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并夺走爵位和土地是正当行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.87,0:15:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是吗  各位魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.67,0:15:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在那之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.09,0:15:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是同盟向提欧•科尔内罗发动了战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.55,0:15:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您该不会想说就算对方打过来了也不能反击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.27,0:15:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被同盟势力包围的情况下自称属于联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.27,0:15:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被打是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.52,0:15:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的意思就是  我阿尔图克被同盟攻打是理所当然的对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.57,0:15:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.24,0:15:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动不动就偷换概念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道森公爵请冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.66,0:15:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就承认先开战的是同盟好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.08,0:15:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 你要是没插手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.29,0:15:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是能跟同盟修复关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.71,0:16:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在瓦尔林德插手之前也许是这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.72,0:16:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德拒绝了有意加入同盟的提欧•科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.89,0:16:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还派出了骑士团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还派出了骑士团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.89,0:16:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  他来向我求援了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.73,0:16:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不答应不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.02,0:16:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为你的一己之见  与同盟的战争才会开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.78,0:16:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.82,0:16:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准狡辩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不答应就得了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.83,0:16:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱着尊重自由与和平的幻想诗联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.42,0:16:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想保护一切加入联合的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.21,0:16:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在场诸位中有人遭到攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.09,0:16:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必定会前去救援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.43,0:16:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来那位海洋王埃里克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.52,0:16:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算进攻保持中立的小大陆布廉特兰德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.69,0:16:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到联合整体情况的话・・・
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.52,0:17:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只能阻止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.61,0:17:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.70,0:17:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护已属于联合势力的塞维斯应该受到指责吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.83,0:17:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位英明的公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.45,0:17:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望诸位能从联合整体的角度来考虑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.21,0:17:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下就定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.67,0:17:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会议的主导权归维拉尔大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经很清楚大家的意见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们幻想诗联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.18,0:17:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将以武力与大工房同盟对决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.76,0:17:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就按照这个方向没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我认为没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.77,0:17:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.73,0:17:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.19,0:17:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我个人倒是不愿与同盟开战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.31,0:17:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我会遵从决议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.03,0:17:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我只想提一个建议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.41,0:17:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当上盟主只是因为父亲是大公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:18:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我认为 应该正式选出一个合适人选当联合的盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.84,0:18:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然现已决定以武力与同盟对决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.80,0:18:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我个人认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.76,0:18:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许阿尔图克伯爵才是联合盟主的合适人选
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.43,0:18:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一旦阿尔图克伯爵确定当上了盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.60,0:18:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意第一个向伯爵效忠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.07,0:18:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是维拉尔・康斯坦斯大公的诞生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.15,0:18:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是我输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.95,0:18:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知故问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.62,0:18:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能获得阿莱克希斯大人的推举是我的荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.21,0:18:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过请容我推辞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.34,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的祖父尤根・克莱榭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.59,0:18:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕不愿看见孙子孙女间的争斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.69,0:19:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.69,0:19:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁血伯爵尤根•克莱榭组建的大工房同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.57,0:19:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻想诗联合是为了对抗它而存在的组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.87,0:19:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而维拉尔大人体内流淌的血液
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.79,0:19:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一半是克莱榭家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.42,0:19:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为哈鲁西亚公爵才是联合盟主的最佳人选
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.30,0:19:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已经将哈鲁西亚公爵选为盟主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.05,0:19:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还是应该推进与同盟的和谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.14,0:19:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟必定不会接受和谈储备战斗力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.93,0:19:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚会攻打过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.14,0:19:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也没问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.40,0:19:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想违抗我们盟主的意向吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.23,0:19:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没承认呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你能当盟主吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.45,0:19:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再确认一遍 大家同意和谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.25,0:20:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.22,0:20:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联合失去了干载难逢的摧毁同盟的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.89,0:20:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次  肯定会堵上威信政打联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.27,0:20:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克能抵挡住吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.44,0:20:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联合的使者带来了和谈的请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.24,0:20:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.32,0:20:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅夺走了塞维斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.24,0:20:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还夺走了弗维斯和克劳维斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.91,0:20:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还想和谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.79,0:20:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会感到愤怒实属正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.58,0:20:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联合说想按照大圣堂惨剧发生前商定好的方针推进谈判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.21,0:20:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是让哈鲁西亚公爵与我结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.80,0:20:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再统一大公家的建议吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.47,0:20:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 这似乎便是联合的盟主阿莱克希斯•德赛的意向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.81,0:21:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知格尔哈德  让那边准备好与斯达尔克开战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他无意归顺我方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.11,0:21:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也打算出战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.48,0:21:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让斯达尔克的归顺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.40,0:21:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为进攻阿尔图克的跳板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.95,0:21:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.36,0:21:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  阿莱克希斯
